---
title: Korma Style Mushroom Curry with roast aubergine and fluffy rice
description: Korma is a curry that's characterised by its creaminess, and this recipe can definitely be described in this way. The dish gets its rich velvety texture not only from the korma paste and coconut milk but also from the addition of peanut butter which is why it's also completely plant-based.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W17_IE_IEXVV0039-3_05_Mainlow-5a3e9645.jpg
